    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Overshoes of rubber, especially those without buckles and not extending as high as the ankle. For overshoes of rubber or waterproof fabric that extend above the ankle and often have buckles or other fasteners, use "galoshes."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Overschoenen van rubber, vooral die zonder gespen en die niet helemaal tot aan de enkel reiken. Gebruik `galoches' voor overschoenen van rubber of waterafstotend materiaal die tot boven de enkel reiken en vaak gespen of andere sluitingen hebben.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052381/Van Dale Engels-Nederlands (1989)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Überschuh aus Gummi, insbesondere diejenigen ohne Schnallen und nicht bis über den Knöchel reichend. Für einen Überschuh aus Gummi oder wasserdichtem Stoff, der über den Knöchel reicht und der oft Schnallen oder andere Verschlüße besitzt, benutzen Sie den Begriff "Galosche".</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>German</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000232/IfM-SMB-PK</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
